			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just another 2cp about this beautiful item...<BR>
<BR>
In the ongoing debate about who's epic is better, you have to remember the fine points.  In Damage standards, yeah, I think the Mage Epic is the best.  The Cleric epic is nowhere near as good, yet just as awesome.  I mean, c'mon!  Yeah, my Mage Epic (when I get it) can kick your arse from here to the Plane of Sky, but what happens when I get trained?<BR>
<BR>
I'll be damned if I'm gonna let myself lose Exp at that level because some dumbassed monk didn't know how to FD.  I want my exp back...And who better than an Epic'd Cleric?  They charge a lot less.  =)<BR>
<BR>
I realize that our quest is one of, if not THE most difficult one in the game, but its worth it, is it not?  I mean, 2 on 1 are never the fairest of odds.  Especially when one has 3200hps, and the other can spell-smack for 1/3 of that in one spell.<BR>
<BR>
So C'Mon, Mr. Wizzy.  Root my pet.  I dare you.  I'll disspell his ass and light you up like a christmas tree while he beats you down like the mana ***** you are.  =)  No hard feelings, though.  Seriously.  And in the future (no pun intended), any Wizzy's my level on Ayonae Ro, send me a tell.  I'll duel ya and buy ya a drink afterwards.  I've always liked the Mage vs Wizzy antagonism.<BR>
<BR>
Future Endeavors<BR>
24th Level Mage<BR>
Ayonae Ro<BR>
&quot;Unless you've known fire raging from your fists, or felt the cold death of a blade in your hand, you have never truly lived.&quot; 
				</font>
